	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Solved!
<br />
<br />This was caused by an stepdown electricity converter that worked with the other games, but not with powerpak.
<br />Anyone else with the same problem, use nintendos official powercable for your country and plug it in to the american nes console.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
